                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7691" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1204</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2991 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">低业绩，高分红：穿透零售巨头-重百“掏空式”分红之谜</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Low performance and high dividend penetrating the retail giant - the mystery of hollowed out dividend of Chongbai</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈利，左雨薇，高骏峰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆百货大楼股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆百货；“掏空式”分红；股利政策；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ChongqingDepartmentStore，“hollow-out”dividend，dividend policy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022年3月25日，重庆百货发布年报，2021年实现营业收入211.24亿元，同比增长0.22%；净利润9.80亿元，同比下降6.68%。然而与此同时，其拟派发现金红利15.01亿元（含税）。这意味着本年度重庆百货现金分红比例高达178.2%，而后发现这是重庆百货连续第二年出现这种情况。在业绩下滑的情况下连续两年的“掏空式分红”引起市场广泛关注与热烈讨论。本案例从梳理重庆百货的发展历程出发，聚焦重庆百货连续两年的高派现事件，结合重庆百货的混改背景，着重分析其巨额派现行为背后的动因及影响因素，最后启发学员思考此种掏空式分红对重庆百货的影响。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">On March 25, 2022, Chongqing Department Store released its annual report. In 2021, its operating income was 21.124 billion yuan, a year-on-year increase of 0.22%; its net profit was 980 million yuan, a year-on-year decrease of 6.68%. However, at the same time, it plans to distribute a cash dividend of 1.501 billion yuan (tax included). This means that the cash dividend ratio of Chongqing Department Store this year is as high as 178.2%, and it is found that this is the second consecutive year that Chongqing Department Store has this situation. In the case of declining performance, the &quot;hollow-out dividend&quot; for two consecutive years has attracted widespread attention and heated discussions in the market. This case starts from sorting out the development history of Chongqing Department Store, focuses on the high distribution event of Chongqing Department Store for two consecutive years, combines the background of Chongqing Department Store&#39;s mixed-ownership reform, focuses on analyzing the motivation and influencing factors behind its huge distribution behavior, and finally inspires students to think about this The impact of hollowed-out dividends on Chongqing Department Store.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
